Nigerian singer, Paul Okoye has celebrated his beautiful wife, Anita Okoye who turned 31 today, November 8. First, the singer took to Instagram to share a stunning photo of the mother of his three children (as seen below). Anita okoye He then wrote: “Happy special birthday to the one and only love of my life  @anita_okoye.. Mama ejima.. I love you ..we all love you ..Blessings always” Fans of the singer have stormed his comment section with messages celebrating the woman. Source